{"tid":871211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無碼】包下露營區拍中出AV　52男女優獲不起訴","createTime":"2018-10-21T17:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T01:39:45.000Z","uid":3189,"like":195,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"e050bd065047355d69693f28f44f1e1a22a5cca8","tid":871211,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"日本知名AV公司「CA」的40歲社長與數十名男女優及工作人員等52人，日前被控在露營區拍中出AV涉及公然猥褻一案，東京地方檢察廳最新裁定指出，這52人獲不起訴處分。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《TBS新聞台》報導，東京地檢署表示，這52人當時的拍攝現場是在山裡，而該處並非是不特定多數人所認識的地方，因此裁定不起訴。案情指出，事發在2013年9月30日與10月1日，當時這群人到相模原市一處公共露營區拍攝A片，有觸犯公然猥褻罪之嫌。但CA社長指出，當時進行拍攝時有將露營場全面包場，並有人員管制，一般民眾是無法入營區內的，否認有觸犯公然猥褻。<br />\n<br />\n台灣網友紛紛表示：「東京地檢強力應援！這片應該會大賣。」、「跪求番號。」、「這部一定要看。」、「日本真是先進國家。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/012429_fda90fa46c601d734a453c4499d66d2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F012429_fda90fa46c601d734a453c4499d66d2a.png&h=ffcf77d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友推測東京地檢署查辦的AV是這一支。<a href=\"http://翻自ttaro.blog.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E8%87%AAttaro.blog.jp&d=6CJtOGdq%2BlGd4BqvTH7incmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=74004c74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻自ttaro.blog.jp</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20160924/955065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20160924%2F955065&d=6CJtOGdq%2BlGd4BqvTH7incmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=85e1d65f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20160924%2F955065&h=5d058977\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20160924/955065</a>"},{"pid":"e8d45f829ff73db9f8c550865ab4ccc36fa86483","tid":871211,"uid":54777,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"52<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" cla